{
  "stem": "13471.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then with the fall semester, I went to Jena, which is in middle-- middle Germany, as you probably are aware, and spent the two winters, winter and spring semesters there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then at the end of that I toured Germany and went to-- went to France.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I liked Germany.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if you know the country.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a beautiful country.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even today, even with this incredible overcrowding that they have there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I liked the basic Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I was horrified at Hitler-ism.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I was more than horrified, I, I was scared.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had read Toynbee's study of civilization.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You're probably familiar with it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was convinced that he had it right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But that Nazism, if it were successful, would undermine this and destroy it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that this must not be allowed to happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was very scornful, of course, of their anti-Semitism, which I took at that point as simply a ploy to gain, how will I say, a majority vote from the German people and get into power.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I didn't really see it in the terrible crime aspect, which we later came to recognize was behind it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I thought, simply-- there are plenty of anti-Semites in the US, always were, had been when I grew up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was familiar with this, this was nothing new.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But then I, I-- but what I saw was, this movement, if it was successful, could spell the end of Western civilization as we knew it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this scared the hell out of me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I came back from Germany-- I don't know if you remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was a great student Lincoln one point.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
